<main>
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="my-5">Join us</h1>
    <p style="max-width: 800px;">Are you passionate about youth participation in policymaking? Are you ready to catalyze youth engagement with key policies to shape our future? <strong>You’re in the right place</strong>, keep reading.</p>
  </div>
  <section class="py-5">
    <div class="container d-flex justify-content-between flex-column flex-lg-row">
      <div class="container-half">
        <h2><mark class="mark-yllw">What's in it for me?</mark></h2>
        <p>We asked ourselves what motivates us to be here. Here are the most common reasons:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Understand policymaking</strong>, and learn about its actors and outcomes</li>
          <li>Work in an <strong>international environment</strong> and meet like-minded people</li>
          <li>The opportunity to <strong>make a difference</strong></li>
          <li>The belief that <strong>policymaking should be more collaborative and inclusive</strong>, and commitment  to increasing awareness and closing the knowledge gap</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="container-half d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhnsnkxbe/image/upload/v1628700838/openpolicyeu/day_dream_ptlngs.png">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container-short">
      <p>In other words… Do you want to learn more about policymaking or help others to do so? Do you fancy a challenge? Do you (warning: cliché sentence coming) want to be the change you wish to see in the world? Then find out how you can contribute:</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
      <h2><mark class="mark-yllw">How can I help?</mark></h2>
      <p>You can help by joining us as a volunteer! Check out our open positions:</p>
      <% if !@policy_positions.empty? %>
        <div class="mt-5">
          <h3><mark class="mark-blue">Policy Analysis</mark> & <mark class="mark-blue">Content creation</mark></h3>
          <% @policy_positions.each do |volunteer_position| %>
            <div id="volunteer_position-<%= volunteer_position.id %>">
              <%= render 'pages/partials/position_closed',
                  volunteer_position: volunteer_position %>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      <% if !@dev_positions.empty? %>
        <div class="mt-5">
          <h3><mark class="mark-blue">Web Development</mark> & <mark class="mark-blue">UX Design</mark></h3>
          <% @dev_positions.each do |volunteer_position| %>
            <div id="volunteer_position-<%= volunteer_position.id %>">
              <%= render 'pages/partials/position_closed',
                  volunteer_position: volunteer_position %>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      <% if !@comms_positions.empty? %>
        <div class="mt-5">
          <h3><mark class="mark-blue">Marketing</mark> & <mark class="mark-blue">Communication</mark></h3>
          <% @comms_positions.each do |volunteer_position| %>
            <div id="volunteer_position-<%= volunteer_position.id %>">
              <%= render 'pages/partials/position_closed',
                  volunteer_position: volunteer_position %>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      <% if !@ambassadors_positions.empty? %>
        <div class="mt-5">
          <h3><mark class="mark-blue">Ambassadors Programme</mark></h3>
          <% @ambassadors_positions.each do |volunteer_position| %>
            <div id="volunteer_position-<%= volunteer_position.id %>">
              <%= render 'pages/partials/position_closed',
                  volunteer_position: volunteer_position %>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      <% if !@partners_positions.empty? %>
        <div class="mt-5">
          <h3><mark class="mark-blue">Partnership</mark></h3>
          <% @partners_positions.each do |volunteer_position| %>
            <div id="volunteer_position-<%= volunteer_position.id %>">
              <%= render 'pages/partials/position_closed',
                  volunteer_position: volunteer_position %>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="container-short py-5">
    <h2><mark class="mark-yllw">How can I join?</mark></h2>
    <p>Please apply by sending an email to <a href="mailto:info@openpolicy.eu" class="text-link">info@openpolicy.eu</a> with your CV. Tell us a bit about yourself and how you would like to contribute to the OpenPolicy Europe project.</p>
    <p>Check above for additional information we might need depending on the position you're applying to.</p>
    <p class="text-center">We look forward to hearing from you!</p>
  </section>
</main>
